flowchart TD
    U[User / Reviewer]
    API[Go API Server<br/>chi router<br/>cmd/server]
    IDX[/POST /index/]
    ANL[/POST /analyze or /ask/]
    EVL[/POST /eval/]

    RAW[(data/raw/*.json<br/>profiles, financials, news, ground_truth)]
    PREP[Data preparation<br/>Fact normalization]
    EMB[Embedding model<br/>Ollama: nomic-embed-text]
    VDB[(Qdrant vector store)]
    RET[RAG retrieval<br/>ticker filter + top-k]
    TOOLS[Tool-calling layer<br/>sentiment, risk, PE]
    REASON[Reasoning prompt<br/>Ollama: llama3]
    REFL[Reflection prompt<br/>self-check/revise]
    OUT["Final decision<br>BUY | HOLD | SELL"]
    METRICS[Evaluation report<br/>accuracy, reasoning quality,<br/>confidence calibration]

    U --> API
    API --> IDX
    API --> ANL
    API --> EVL

    IDX --> RAW --> PREP --> EMB --> VDB

    ANL --> RET
    RET --> EMB
    RET --> VDB
    RET --> TOOLS
    TOOLS --> REASON --> REFL --> OUT

    EVL --> RET
    EVL --> RAW
    EVL --> METRICS

    subgraph Technologies
      T1[Go 1.26]
      T2[chi v5]
      T3[Ollama]
      T4[Qdrant]
      T5[Docker Compose]
      T6[Testify]
    end

    API -.built with.-> T1
    API -.router.-> T2
    EMB -.served by.-> T3
    REASON -.served by.-> T3
    VDB -.engine.-> T4
    API -.run via.-> T5
    METRICS -.tests via.-> T6
